===message:There is one thing I have seen in several posts - "misuse of power" when describing the Anti-federalists point of view.  I agree with this, there was definitely reason to believe this would happen, considering the events that took place under the British government.  However, don’t we have (or have had) numerous politicians that have misused their power!  Hindsight is always 20/20; although, letting the states govern themselves would never gotten this country to where it is now.
